Package spaska.data.readers

A package containing the readers that transform the outside data into our DataSet format.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InputReader
    An input reader represents classes that will be able to read datasets from different sources.
    Validator
    An interface that represents the validators in the framework.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractInputReader
    This is a convenient base class for InputReader.
    ARFFInputReader
    An input reader that reads from ARFF files.
    NormalizeValidator
    A simple preprocessor/validator that will normalize the input values to be in the [downLimit, upperLimit].
